gobblin.publisher

Class CommitSequencePublisher

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.publisher.DataPublisher
      • gobblin.publisher.SingleTaskDataPublisher
        • gobblin.publisher.BaseDataPublisher
          • gobblin.publisher.CommitSequencePublisher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable

    @Alpha
public class CommitSequencePublisher
extends BaseDataPublisher
    An implementation of DataPublisher for exactly-once delivery.

    This publisher does not actually publish data, instead it constructs a CommitSequence.Builder. The builder is used by Gobblin runtime to build a CommitSequence, which is then persisted and executed.
